            <description><![CDATA[
<h3>First release</h3>
<ul>
<li>Search GIFs from the menu bar and copy any of them to the clipboard with a click.</li>
<li>Bring your own free Giphy key.</li>
<li>Star the ones you like; Quip keeps the GIFs you've copied and your recent searches close by.</li>
<li>A narrow and a wide layout, start at login, and automatic updates.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
